(27150, 257, '_sss|sss_student_message|1|0|value', 'I am currently working in the construction industry and facing difficulties in using computers. Therefore, I decided to join a coaching program where the teacher focuses on my specific requirements and teaches me what I need for my job. NBCC is the best place to learn how to apply computer skills in an industrial setting and how to solve computer-related problems in this context. The teacher can revise topics and conduct daily assessments, ensuring that I never forget the concepts. Thank you so much, sir, for this excellent teaching.'),
(27151, 257, '_sss|sss_designation|1|0|value', 'Construction Engineer'),
