(28495, 258, '_sss|sss_student_name|2|0|value', 'Karan Dadhich'),
(28496, 258, '_sss|sss_course_name|2|0|value', 'Web Design Pro'),
(28497, 258, '_sss|sss_student_message|2|0|value', 'First of all, thank you, sir, for teaching me. I may not have the perfect words, but I\'ll do my best to express it. Sir\'s teaching style is excellent. He explains concepts using the board, and it really works. He teaches you to create a mental image. The classes are very good. If you\'re interested, he will guide you through every aspect. Overall, the coaching is excellent, especially when you have a great teacher. The rest is up to you.\r\n<br>\r\nThe right opportunities at the right time always pay off.'),
