(58, 1, '2023-11-27 16:13:45', '2023-11-27 16:13:45', 'Welcome to our AI ChatGPT Course  a captivating journey into the realm of artificial intelligence! Imagine AI as a super-smart friend that can understand and answer your questions. In this course, we\'ll uncover the intriguing history of AI, from its early days to the powerful ChatGPT technology we have today.\r\n\r\nWhy dive into the world of AI? Because it\'s like having a digital friend that can help you with homework, answer your curious questions, and even have a chat with you! We\'ll explore why AI is a game-changer, making our digital experiences more personalized and efficient.\r\n\r\nEver wonder how AI understands us so well? We\'ll unveil the secrets of natural language processing, the magic that lets AI chat with us just like a real person. And just like learning secret codes for computers, you\'ll discover the fascinating algorithms that make AI conversations so smooth.\r\n\r\nBut the adventure doesn\'t stop there! Get ready to create your own AI magic as we explore hands-on projects. You\'ll learn how to train AI models and even build your own chatbot. It\'s like having your own digital sidekick!\r\n\r\nJoin us on this AI expedition where the past, present, and future of artificial intelligence come together. Enroll now to embark on a journey of discovery, play, and become an AI wizard! Get ready to shape the future with your newfound AI skills!', 'AI (ChatGPT) Pro', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ai-chatgpt-pro', '', '', '2024-01-13 19:10:35', '2024-01-13 19:10:35', '', 0, 'http://localhost/nbcc/?post_type=courses&#038;p=58', 0, 'courses', '', 0),
