(69, 1, '2023-11-27 16:48:38', '2023-11-27 16:48:38', '<div class=\"flex-1 overflow-hidden\">\r\n<div class=\"react-scroll-to-bottom--css-nezis-79elbk h-full\">\r\n<div class=\"react-scroll-to-bottom--css-nezis-1n7m0yu\">\r\n<div class=\"flex flex-col text-sm gizmo:pb-9 dark:bg-gray-800 gizmo:dark:bg-transparent\">\r\n<div class=\"w-full text-token-text-primary border-b border-black/10 gizmo:border-0 dark:border-gray-900/50 gizmo:dark:border-0 bg-gray-50 gizmo:bg-transparent dark:bg-[#444654] gizmo:dark:bg-transparent\" data-testid=\"conversation-turn-7\">\r\n<div class=\"p-4 gizmo:py-2 justify-center text-base md:gap-6 md:py-6 m-auto\">\r\n<div class=\"flex flex-1 gap-4 text-base mx-auto md:gap-6 gizmo:gap-3 gizmo:md:px-5 gizmo:lg:px-1 gizmo:xl:px-5 md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-[38rem] gizmo:md:max-w-3xl gizmo:lg:max-w-[40rem] gizmo:xl:max-w-[48rem] xl:max-w-3xl } group final-completion\">\r\n<div class=\"relative flex w-[calc(100%-50px)] flex-col gizmo:w-full lg:w-[calc(100%-115px)] agent-turn\">\r\n<div class=\"flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3\">\r\n<div class=\"flex flex-grow flex-col max-w-full gap-3 gizmo:gap-0\">\r\n<div class=\"min-h-[20px] text-message flex flex-col items-start gap-3 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5 overflow-x-auto\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"f63838b0-ce6f-4657-b690-e10a2b1e251d\">\r\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark\">\r\n\r\nWelcome to our computer adventure! Imagine computers are like super smart friends helping us do cool things. In our course, we\'ll learn their amazing history from long ago to now.\r\n\r\nWhy do we need to know about computers? Because they\'re like magical tools that make life easier! We\'ll discover how they help us talk to friends, learn new things, and even draw funny pictures.\r\n\r\nEver heard of the internet? It\'s like a big playground for computers where they share all kinds of interesting stuff. And guess what? We\'ll also learn secret codes called \"shortcut keys\" that make using computers super fast and easy.\r\n\r\nBut that\'s not all! We\'ll become computer superheroes by learning special skills with Word, Excel, and PowerPoint. It\'s like having a digital superpower to write stories, count numbers, and make awesome presentations!\r\n\r\nCome join the fun  our computer adventure is waiting for you! Get ready to discover, play, and become a computer genius!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Advanced Computer Course', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '54-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-11-27 16:48:38', '2023-11-27 16:48:38', '', 54, 'http://localhost/nbcc/?p=69', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(70, 1, '2023-11-27 16:51:11', '2023-11-27 16:51:11', 'Welcome to our Advanced Computer Course  where the magic of computing unfolds before your eyes! Picture computers as incredible problem-solving wizards that have evolved over time. In this journey, we\'ll explore their fascinating history, tracing their roots from simple calculators to the powerful machines we use today.\r\n\r\nWhy should you care about computers? Because they\'re not just tools; they\'re like digital companions that make our lives smarter and more efficient. We\'ll unravel their importance in communication, innovation, and daily tasks, understanding why computer awareness is a superpower in the modern world.\r\n\r\nVenture into the realm of the internet  a vast digital universe where computers connect and share information. Uncover the shortcuts, or secret codes, that make interacting with computers a breeze, enhancing your efficiency and speed in navigating the digital landscape.\r\n\r\nBut that\'s not the end of our exploration. Become a digital maestro as we delve into Microsoft Office applications like Word, Excel, and PowerPoint. These tools are like your Swiss army knife for creating documents, crunching numbers, and crafting powerful presentations.\r\n\r\nReady to elevate your computer prowess? Join us on this advanced adventure, where technology meets creativity, and where you\'ll emerge with skills to conquer the digital realm! Enroll now and unlock the doors to a world of endless possibilities.', 'Advanced Computer Course', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '54-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-11-27 16:51:11', '2023-11-27 16:51:11', '', 54, 'http://localhost/nbcc/?p=70', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
