(101, 1, '2023-12-23 01:54:47', '2023-12-23 01:54:47', 'Welcome to<b>New Balaji Computer Classes (NBCC)</b>, your gateway to a world of digital knowledge and technological empowerment.<b>Established in 1st April, 2021</b>, we are dedicated to providing top-notch computer education and training to help you excel in today\'s tech-driven world.\r\n\r\nComputers have become exceedingly useful in today\'s world. The use of computers has proliferated across various sectors, including government offices, banks, schools, colleges, and markets. This is why computer education has become essential in today\'s day and age. Many computer institutes in the market offer courses merely for certificates, which ends up being a waste of both your money and time.\r\n\r\nWe, at New Balaji Computer Classes, offer a comprehensive computer course that not only equips you with essential computer skills but also ensures that you retain and apply this knowledge. Learning computer skills can empower you to digitize your business and even start a new one. New Balaji Computer Classes provides specialized computer courses to cater to your needs, offering complete computer knowledge at an affordable price.', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-12-23 01:54:47', '2023-12-23 01:54:47', '', 8, 'http://localhost/nbcc/?p=101', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(102, 1, '2023-12-23 02:15:34', '2023-12-23 02:15:34', 'Welcome to our WordPress Design and Development Course  an immersive exploration into the dynamic realm of website creation and customization. Tailored for aspiring designers and developers, this course will equip you with the skills needed to craft stunning and functional websites using the powerful WordPress platform.\r\n\r\nUnlock the secrets of WordPress design as we delve into the art of creating visually appealing and user-friendly interfaces. Learn to harness the potential of themes and templates, transforming your ideas into captivating online experiences. Dive into customization, understanding how to make your mark in the digital landscape.\r\n\r\nTransition seamlessly into WordPress development, where coding meets creativity. Master the essentials of HTML, CSS, and PHP to tailor websites to your unique specifications. Explore the world of plugins, understanding how to extend the functionality of your sites with ease.\r\n\r\nOur hands-on approach ensures that you not only comprehend the intricacies of WordPress but also gain practical skills in designing and developing websites. From crafting responsive layouts to optimizing for search engines, this course empowers you to navigate the full spectrum of web design and development within the WordPress ecosystem.\r\n\r\nJoin us on this transformative journey, where creativity meets functionality, and where you\'ll emerge with the expertise to build impactful websites. Enroll now to shape the digital landscape through WordPress design and development!', 'Wordpress Pro (Design + Dev)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '48-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-12-23 02:15:34', '2023-12-23 02:15:34', '', 48, 'http://localhost/nbcc/?p=102', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
