(195, 1, '2024-01-01 17:11:04', '2024-01-01 17:11:04', 'Welcome to our Advanced Web Design Course  a comprehensive exploration of the dynamic world where creativity meets technology, designed for learners seeking expertise in building exceptional websites. In this course, we\'ll dive into the essential building blocks of web design, encompassing HTML, CSS, SASS, and JavaScript.\r\n\r\nUnleash your creativity as we delve into the fundamentals of HTML, the language that forms the backbone of every web page. Learn to structure content seamlessly, turning your ideas into visually stunning and well-organized digital experiences.\r\n\r\nMaster the art of styling with CSS, transforming your HTML creations into visually appealing designs. Elevate your skills with SASS, a powerful extension of CSS, offering advanced features and flexibility to streamline your style sheets and enhance design efficiency.\r\n\r\nVenture into the realm of JavaScript, the language that breathes life into web pages. Explore interactive elements, dynamic content, and responsive design techniques, empowering you to create user-friendly and engaging websites.\r\n\r\nOur hands-on approach ensures that theoretical knowledge seamlessly integrates with practical skills. From crafting responsive layouts to implementing cutting-edge design trends, you\'ll be well-equipped to bring your web design visions to life.\r\n\r\nJoin us on this transformative journey, where the artistry of design meets the precision of coding. Enroll now to acquire the skills that define the modern web designer, and let\'s build the future of the digital landscape together!', 'Web Designing Pro', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '45-revision-v1', '', '', '2024-01-01 17:11:04', '2024-01-01 17:11:04', '', 45, 'http://localhost/nbcc/?p=195', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
