(226, 1, '2024-01-04 15:58:58', '2024-01-04 15:58:58', 'Welcome to our Advanced Computer Course  where the magic of computing unfolds before your eyes! Picture computers as incredible problem-solving wizards that have evolved over time. In this journey, we\'ll explore their fascinating history, tracing their roots from simple calculators to the powerful machines we use today.\r\n\r\nWhy should you care about computers? Because they\'re not just tools; they\'re like digital companions that make our lives smarter and more efficient. We\'ll unravel their importance in communication, innovation, and daily tasks, understanding why computer awareness is a superpower in the modern world.\r\n\r\nVenture into the realm of the internet  a vast digital universe where computers connect and share information. Uncover the shortcuts, or secret codes, that make interacting with computers a breeze, enhancing your efficiency and speed in navigating the digital landscape.\r\n\r\nBut that\'s not the end of our exploration. Become a digital maestro as we delve into Microsoft Office applications like Word, Excel, and PowerPoint. These tools are like your Swiss army knife for creating documents, crunching numbers, and crafting powerful presentations.\r\n\r\nReady to elevate your computer prowess? Join us on this advanced adventure, where technology meets creativity, and where you\'ll emerge with skills to conquer the digital realm! Enroll now and unlock the doors to a world of endless possibilities.', 'Advanced Computer Course', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '54-revision-v1', '', '', '2024-01-04 15:58:58', '2024-01-04 15:58:58', '', 54, 'http://localhost/nbcc/?p=226', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(228, 1, '2024-01-04 16:27:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Welcome to<b>New Balaji Computer Classes (NBCC)</b>, your gateway to a world of digital knowledge and technological empowerment.<b>Established in 1st April, 2021</b>, we are dedicated to providing top-notch computer education and training to help you excel in today\'s tech-driven world.\r\n\r\nComputers have become exceedingly useful in today\'s world. The use of computers has proliferated across various sectors, including government offices, banks, schools, colleges, and markets. This is why computer education has become essential in today\'s day and age. Many computer institutes in the market offer courses merely for certificates, which ends up being a waste of both your money and time.\r\n\r\nWe, at New Balaji Computer Classes, offer a comprehensive computer course that not only equips you with essential computer skills but also ensures that you retain and apply this knowledge. Learning computer skills can empower you to digitize your business and even start a new one. New Balaji Computer Classes provides specialized computer courses to cater to your needs, offering complete computer knowledge at an affordable price.', 'Home', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', '', '', '', '2024-01-04 16:27:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/nbcc/?page_id=228', 0, 'page', '', 0),
