(257, 1, '2024-01-12 16:59:34', '2024-01-12 16:59:34', 'Welcome to<b>New Balaji Computer Classes (NBCC)</b>, your gateway to a world of digital knowledge and technological empowerment.<b>Established in 1st April, 2021</b>, we are dedicated to providing top-notch computer education and training to help you excel in today\'s tech-driven world.\r\n\r\nComputers have become exceedingly useful in today\'s world. The use of computers has proliferated across various sectors, including government offices, banks, schools, colleges, and markets. This is why computer education has become essential in today\'s day and age. Many computer institutes in the market offer courses merely for certificates, which ends up being a waste of both your money and time.\r\n\r\nWe, at New Balaji Computer Classes, offer a comprehensive computer course that not only equips you with essential computer skills but also ensures that you retain and apply this knowledge. Learning computer skills can empower you to digitize your business and even start a new one. New Balaji Computer Classes provides specialized computer courses to cater to your needs, offering complete computer knowledge at an affordable price.', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2024-01-12 16:59:34', '2024-01-12 16:59:34', '', 8, 'http://localhost/nbcc/?p=257', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
